ink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 25, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104vwy1665702614709.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vwy1665702614709.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vwy1665702614709.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"vwy1665702614709\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Controls whether forms are automatically maximized when they do not fit in the\n      application window. This setting also controls whether a component that was previously\n      maximized is maximized again when it is run again.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"vwy1665702614709__topic_d146219e1_d146220e1_d146221e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vwy1665702614709__p_d146222e1_d146223e1_d146224e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">AutoMaximize</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">on</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">off</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"vwy1665702614709__section_w3341ab1b5b3_w3342ab1b5_w3343ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"vwy1665702614709__table_d17861e1_d17862e1_d17863e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">off</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">File section</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yzj1665702614359.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yzj1665702614359.html\" title=\"The [upi] section of the initialization file determines the appearance or behavior of many Universal Presentation Interface (UPI) objects under Microsoft Windows.\">[upi]</a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vwy1665702614709__section_trs_yb4_yvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d221228e109\">Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"vwy1665702614709__table_d17864e1_d17865e1_d17866e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vwy1665702614709__table_d17864e1_d17865e1_d17866e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vwy1665702614709__table_d17864e1_d17865e1_d17866e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vwy1665702614709__table_d17864e1_d17865e1_d17866e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">on</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vwy1665702614709__table_d17864e1_d17865e1_d17866e1__entry__2\">Form components are automatically\n                        maximized</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vwy1665702614709__table_d17864e1_d17865e1_d17866e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">off</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vwy1665702614709__table_d17864e1_d17865e1_d17866e1__entry__2\">Form components are not automatically\n                        maximized, unless the Quick Zoom function is used.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vwy1665702614709__section_igs_bc4_yvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d221228e161\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">This option only works when the form runs in a startup shell and the\n               <span class=\"keyword option\">LayoutStorage</span> (<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Layout State Storage</span>) setting\n            is on.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oix1665702652724.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Layout State Storage (LAYOUTSTORAGE)</a><p>Determines how the layout state for forms and grid widgets is stored. Valid values are PROCESS, COMPONENT, or INSTANCE.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533223\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533223\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "AutoMaximize Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 25, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Controls whether forms are automatically maximized when they do not fit in the application window. This setting also controls whether a component that was previously maximized is maximized again when it is run again. AutoMaximize = on | off Default value off File section [upi] Values Value Description on Form components are automatically maximized off Form components are not automatically maximized, unless the Quick Zoom function is used. Description This option only works when the form runs in a startup shell and the LayoutStorage ( Layout State Storage ) setting is on. Related Links Layout State Storage (LAYOUTSTORAGE) Determines how the layout state for forms and grid widgets is stored. Valid values are PROCESS, COMPONENT, or INSTANCE. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}